# ChangeLog for x11-base/xorg-server
# Copyright 1999-2015 Gentoo Foundation; Distributed under the GPL v2
# $Header: /var/cvsroot/gentoo-x86/x11-base/xorg-server/ChangeLog,v 1.854 2015/07/15 20:56:08 zlogene Exp $

  15 Jul 2015; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r5.ebuild:
  ia64 stable wrt bug #548002

*xorg-server-1.17.2 (10 Jul 2015)

  10 Jul 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +xorg-server-1.17.2.ebuild:
  Version bump. See bug #551680.

  03 Jul 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r5.ebuild:
  Stable for alpha, wrt bug #548002

  24 Jun 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r5.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #548002

  17 Jun 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r5.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #548002

  14 Jun 2015; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r5.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #548002

  13 Jun 2015; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r5.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #548002

  13 Jun 2015; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r5.ebuild:
  amd64 stable wrt bug #548002

  13 Jun 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r5.ebuild:
  Stable for PPC64 (bug #548002).

*xorg-server-1.12.4-r5 (28 Apr 2015)

  28 Apr 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  +files/xorg-server-1.12-cve-2015-3418.patch, +xorg-server-1.12.4-r5.ebuild:
  Add fix for security bug #548002.

  31 Mar 2015; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r4.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild, xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.16.4-r1.ebuild, xorg-server-1.16.4-r2.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.17.1.ebuild, xorg-server-1.17.1-r1.ebuild:
  Update dependency after package move of eselect modules to app-eselect.

  17 Mar 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild:
  Apply libXfont dependency changes to 1.15 too

  17 Mar 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  xorg-server-1.12.4-r4.ebuild, xorg-server-1.17.1-r1.ebuild:
  Update dependencies to explicitly state compatibility with libXfont versions.
  Restore arm64 keyword that was apparently dropped due to mistake.

  17 Mar 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  -xorg-server-1.12.4-r3.ebuild, -xorg-server-1.15.2-r1.ebuild,
  -xorg-server-1.16.3-r1.ebuild, -xorg-server-1.16.3.ebuild,
  -xorg-server-1.17.0.ebuild:
  Remove vulnerable versions, security bug #539692.

  14 Mar 2015; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #530652

  14 Mar 2015; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #530652

  14 Mar 2015; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r4.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #530652

  06 Mar 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #530652).

  03 Mar 2015; Yixun Lan <dlan@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.17.1.ebuild:
  add arm64 support, tested on A53 board

*xorg-server-1.16.4-r2 (28 Feb 2015)

  28 Feb 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +xorg-server-1.16.4-r2.ebuild:
  Backport the eselect-opengl/Files section fix to 1.16* branch.

*xorg-server-1.17.1-r1 (27 Feb 2015)

  27 Feb 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
  +files/xorg-server-1.17-support-multiple-Files-sections.patch,
  +xorg-server-1.17.1-r1.ebuild:
  Add support for multiple "Files" sections as needed for eselect-opengl, bug
  #541232.

  24 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r4.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild, xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild:
  Stable for alpha, wrt bug #530652

  23 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r4.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild, xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #530652

  22 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r4.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild, xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #530652

  22 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.17.1.ebuild:
  Require at least libdrm 2.4.46 for modesetting.

  22 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.17.1.ebuild:
  Add proper dependencies for IUSE=xephyr, bug 528230.

  21 Feb 2015; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.17.0.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.17.1.ebuild:
  Increase xinit dependency, bug 536756.

  21 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r4.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild, xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #530652

  20 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r4.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild, xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #530652

  19 Feb 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  xorg-server-1.16.4-r1.ebuild, xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild:
  Remove reference to non-existent upgrade guide, bug #540584.

  19 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r4.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild, xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #530652

  18 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xorg-server-1.12.4-r4.ebuild,
  xorg-server-1.15.2-r2.ebuild, xorg-server-1.16.4.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #530652

