*xorg-server-1.16.2.901-r1 (11 Dec 2014)

  11 Dec 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
  +xorg-server-1.16.2.901-r1.ebuild:
  Port the new eselect-opengl support to the new version, to help solving
  blockers for ugrade.

*xorg-server-1.16.2.901 (09 Dec 2014)

  09 Dec 2014; Rémi Cardona <remi@gentoo.org> +xorg-server-1.16.2.901.ebuild:
  Bump to 1.16.2.901 (without Michał's eselect-opengl overhaul).

*xorg-server-1.16.2-r1 (08 Dec 2014)

  08 Dec 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +xorg-server-1.16.2-r1.ebuild:
  Update to work with new eselect-opengl, bug #531842.

*xorg-server-1.16.2 (15 Nov 2014)

  15 Nov 2014; Rémi Cardona <remi@gentoo.org> +xorg-server-1.16.2.ebuild:
